                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14409306" author="jdcasey" created="Wed, 9 Nov 2005 21:41:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;hmm, bring up an interesting point:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;How can we determine the actual version of a system-scoped dependency?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409323" author="jdcasey" created="Wed, 9 Nov 2005 22:34:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;it doesn&apos;t make sense to have a version range for a system-scoped dependency, unless you can check the version of the artifact on the system for a match. Since we can&apos;t reliably do this, I&apos;m disabling version-range checking for system-scoped deps, and using either the recommendedVersion or &quot;unknown&quot; for cases where getVersion() == null.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It&apos;s beginning to be apparent that system-scoped deps are a wrong decision. I think we&apos;ll start phasing them out when we have better spec-dependency support...they represent too many questions that fall outside the main framework of maven, and I believe they&apos;re unnecessary.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409260" author="brettporter" created="Thu, 10 Nov 2005 00:36:33 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fix broke the build, rolled back&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;(to reapply, run &lt;br/&gt;
  svn merge -r332219:332220&lt;br/&gt;
in maven-artifact after updating)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409391" author="carlos" created="Thu, 10 Nov 2005 01:13:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Currently they are just an advice to people, eg they need java 1.4.x tools.jar&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14409309" author="jdcasey" created="Mon, 14 Nov 2005 19:54:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;rolled these changes back in, and fixed faulty logic that was causing the failure. The problem was that I had it stopping the recursion before it had processed the system-scoped dep, rather than right below it...&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17996862" author="JIRAUSER302100" created="Sat, 5 Jul 2025 08:32:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven/issues/3223&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven#3223&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
